Guided by the ethos of minimal impact on the environment, the many initiatives of ITC Sonar and ITC Royal Bengal are brought to light by sustain textile fashion designer @paromitabanerjee 

From representing India at the UN ‘Fashion for the Development and Peace’ show in Shanghai to being part of leading Fashion Weeks in the country since 2009, this brand has journeyed 10 years in the fashion industry. 

Join one of the pioneers of sustainable fashion in the country as she takes you through the properties elaborating on the processes that go into living up to that ethos.

With #OnlyOneEarth to nurture and protect, ITC Royal Bengal and ITC Sonar wish you a Happy World Environment Day!

Be it our ongoing recycling initiative and elimination of single-use plastics within the hotel, or ITC Sonar’s certification on becoming the first hotel in the world to be issued Carbon Credits from UNFCCC, each sustainable practice reflects our commitment to providing #ResponsibleLuxury.

With the world's first three LEED Zero Carbon* Certified hotels, #ITCHotels welcomes you to experiences that let you #LoveNatureLiveZero

Lather, rinse, and repeat to keep diseases at bay - we wish you a Happy Hygiene Day. 

In keeping with the spirit of #ResponsibleLuxury, ITC Royal Bengal and ITC Sonar have always fostered the habit of clean hands with healthier practices. 

By engaging in skits, documentary screenings, poster-making competitions, and quizzes, we aim to break the germ cycle and encourage the habit of cleaning one’s hands frequently.

For more information, please call 033 4446 4646

#ITCRoyalBengal #ITCSonar #ITCHotels #ResponsibleLuxury #WeAssure #HandHygieneDay #HandHygiene #Safety #Kolkata

Don’t let your greens disappear, invest in the earth!

Rooted in the spirit of #ResponsibleLuxury, our LEED Platinum Green Hotels are lending a hand to save the land we share by recycling 100% of its biodegradable and non-biodegradable waste, reducing carbon emissions, utilizing renewable sources for energy demand, and eliminating single-use plastic products to inspire hope for generations to come. 

We at ITC Royal Bengal & ITC Sonar wish you a Happy Earth Day!
